&lt;p&gt;Specialist Community Mental Health Clinical Pharmacists - Secondment/Fixed Term 2 years&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for one specialist mental pharmacist to support development of pharmacy service within community mental health teams. To provide specialist clinical pharmacy in a specific area of clinical and/or operational practice, to support the medicines-related care of patients, support the provision and development of medicines management services and to participate in training, education and research as required.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Previous applicants need not apply&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Benefits:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Season Ticket Loans&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;NHS discounts for staff&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent Training facilities and opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The opportunity to work bank shifts and expand knowledge and experience in other areas&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Salary Sacrifice schemes including lease cars and Cycle to Work&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Buying and Selling annual leave scheme&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Zainab Al-Rubie&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;zainab.al-rubie@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
